OL,3,CNigel Farage offered Sunderland
OL,4,CStadium of Light visit by club director
OL,6,FThe Reform UK leader Nigel Farage has
OL,7,Fbeen invited to visit Sunderland AFC's
OL,8,Fhome ground.
OL,10,FFarage's visit was due to take place
OL,11,Fthis week, according to Reform UK
OL,12,Fsources, just days after a similar
OL,13,Fappearance at Ipswich Town, which was
OL,14,Fcondemned by some supporters' groups.
OL,16,FThe Reform UK leader was in Sunderland
OL,17,Fthis week to launch his party's local
OL,18,Felection campaign.
OL,20,FFarage says he hopes to attend a home
OL,21,Ffixture in the coming weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
