OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774627872
OL,3,CNigel Farage offered Sunderland
OL,4,CStadium of Light visit by club director
OL,6,F"I've been talking to one of the
OL,7,Fdirectors, and they'd very much like
OL,8,Fto see me there for a home game,"
OL,9,FFarage told ITV News.
OL,11,F"If I can make it, I will."
OL,13,FSunderland AFC were approached for
OL,14,Fcomment.
OL,16,FITV News understands Juan Sartori is
OL,17,Fthe Sunderland AFC director who
OL,18,Fextended the invitation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@aO]sD@AOUsD@[O]
