OL,3,CNigel Farage offered Sunderland
OL,4,CStadium of Light visit by club director
OL,6,FSartori owns a 34% stake in the club
OL,7,Falongside the club's chairman and
OL,8,Fmajority shareholder, Kyril Louis-
OL,9,FDreyfus, who owns 64%.
OL,11,FFarage had hoped to visit the Stadium
OL,12,Fof Light this week, according to
OL,13,FReform UK sources, but the meeting was
OL,14,Fnever formally arranged.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
