OL,3,CNigel Farage offered Sunderland
OL,4,CStadium of Light visit by club director
OL,6,FHe entered politics in 2019 when he
OL,7,Ffinished runner-up in the race to lead
OL,8,FUruguay's right-wing National Party
OL,9,Fahead of the country's presidential
OL,10,Felection. The 45-year-old was elected
OL,11,Fto Uruguay's Senate in October that
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,FSartori became a minority shareholder
OL,15,Fin Sunderland AFC in 2018 after being
OL,16,Fintroduced to the club by former
OL,17,Fowners Stewart Donald and Charlie
OL,18,FMethven.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
