OL,3,CNigel Farage offered Sunderland
OL,4,CStadium of Light visit by club director
OL,6,FEarlier this week, Farage sparked
OL,7,Fcontroversy after visiting another
OL,8,Ffootball club, Ipswich Town.
OL,10,FFarage posed for photos in the club's
OL,11,Fdressing room and media suite, and
OL,12,Frecorded a pitchside party political
OL,13,Fvideo at Portman Road, the
OL,14,Fchampionship club's stadium.
OL,16,FHis appearance sparked a backlash from
OL,17,Fsome Ipswich Town fan groups, who said
OL,18,FIpswich Town "risked alienating large
OL,19,Fnumbers of the fanbase and fomenting
OL,20,Fdivision".
OL,26,@zD@NOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
