PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774627872
OL,3,CNigel Farage offered Sunderland
OL,4,CStadium of Light visit by club director
OL,6,F"Clubs should want to talk to me,"
OL,7,FFarage told ITV News during his visit
OL,8,Fto Sunderland.
OL,10,F"The government is about to bring in a
OL,11,Fregulator and I think the last thing
OL,12,FEnglish football needs - given what a
OL,13,Fmassive success the Premier League -
OL,14,Fis a state appointed regulator.
OL,16,F"It's a conversation I had at Ipswich
OL,17,Fthe other day and I'll have at
OL,18,FSunderland before very long and I want
OL,19,Fto speak to all the clubs about this."
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@bO]rD@AOUxD@AOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
