OL,3,CNigel Farage offered Sunderland
OL,4,CStadium of Light visit by club director
OL,6,FFarage denied he was being endorsed by
OL,7,FSunderland AFC. "It's not about
OL,8,Fsupport," he said. "It's about a
OL,9,Ffootball club being open to leaders of
OL,10,Fnational political parties."
OL,12,F"I've been talking to one of the
OL,13,Fdirectors and they'd very much like to
OL,14,Fsee me there," said Farage about
OL,15,FSunderland AFC.
OL,26,@oD@QOUpD@IO]pD@TOUrD@\O]
