OL,3,CNigel Farage offered Sunderland
OL,4,CStadium of Light visit by club director
OL,6,FEngland's Independent Football
OL,7,FRegulator was established by the
OL,8,Fgovernment last year. The body - which
OL,9,Fis independent from government and
OL,10,Ffootball authorities - aims to improve
OL,11,Ffinancial sustainability in the
OL,12,Ffootball pyramid, stop clubs from
OL,13,Fjoining breakaway competitions and
OL,14,Ftoughen up tests to stop rogue owners.
OL,16,FThe Premier League and some club
OL,17,Fexecutives criticised its introduction
OL,18,Fand questioned the need for a
OL,19,Fregulator.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
