OL,3,CNigel Farage offered Sunderland
OL,4,CStadium of Light visit by club director
OL,6,FReform UK have increasingly tried to
OL,7,Fappeal to football supporters in the
OL,8,FUK. Last year, the party launched its
OL,9,Fown light-blue football strip with
OL,10,F'Farage 10' printed on the back and
OL,11,Fparty logo and union flag on the front.
OL,13,FReform's equalities spokesperson,
OL,14,FSuella Braverman MP, this week wrote
OL,15,Fto the Football Association to
OL,16,Fcriticise the governing body's
OL,17,Fdiversity policies, which the former
OL,18,FConservative Home Secretary called
OL,19,F"utter woke nonsense".
